metadata.name: Unravel People's FIDENZA
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's FIDENZA, which represents an inactive state of pFIDENZA. Users can participate in a new Fidenza acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's FIDENZA as credit. upFIDENZA can be claimed into pFIDENZA when the subscription successfully acquires a new Fidenza.
